Dieter Brummer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dieter_Brummer 0 Dieter Kirk Brummer (born 5 May 1976 in Sydney) is an Australian actor of German descent, probably best known for his role as Shane Parrish, from 1992 until 1996 on the television soap opera Home and Away.
